      • createMetadata

        public abstract boolean createMetadata()
                                throws Exception
        Concrete subclasses should implement to create metadata if it does not already exist. Return value should indicate as appropriate.
        Returns:
        true if metadata was created, or false if metadata already existed and so creation was bypassed.
        Throws:
        Exception - if there is a problem creating metadata.
